---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Kicker from "@/components/fundations/elements/Kicker.astro";
import Button from "@/components/fundations/elements/Button.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section>
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <Kicker variant="default">SERVICE 1 OF 4</Kicker>
        <Text
          tag="h1"
          variant="displayLG"
          class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight mt-8 font-display"
        >
          AI Readiness Diagnostic
        </Text>
        <Text
          tag="p"
          variant="textBase"
          class="text-base-600 lg:text-balance mt-6 text-pretty"
        >
          The entry point. Assessment before investment. Before you spend $50K–$200K on AI deployment, spend 2 weeks understanding whether your organization is ready to adopt it.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT MAKES THIS DIFFERENT -->
  <section class="border-t border-base-200">
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-16">
      <Text
        tag="h2"
        variant="displayMD"
        class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight font-display"
      >
        What Makes This Different
      </Text>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
        <div class="p-8 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-red-900 font-medium">
            Standard AI consulting approach:
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-red-800">
            <li>• Vendor demonstrates tool</li>
            <li>• Technical team validates accuracy</li>
            <li>• Procurement approves budget</li>
            <li>• Deploy to 500 users</li>
            <li class="font-medium mt-3">Result: 18% adoption, tool sits unused</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-green-900 font-medium">
            HCAIF Diagnostic approach:
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-green-800">
            <li>• Assess current readiness across 5 dimensions</li>
            <li>• Build driver trees to identify root causes</li>
            <li>• Model adoption-adjusted ROI (not vendor ROI)</li>
            <li>• Prioritize capability-building over technology procurement</li>
            <li class="font-medium mt-3">Result: Deploy when organization is ready, achieve 60–75% adoption</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <Text
        tag="p"
        variant="textBase"
        class="text-base-900 font-medium mt-8"
      >
        The difference: We tell you whether to deploy now, build capability first, or redesign the initiative entirely.
      </Text>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>

  <!-- HCAIF FRAMEWORK -->
  <section class="border-t border-base-200 bg-base-50">
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-16">
      <Text
        tag="h2"
        variant="displayMD"
        class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight font-display"
      >
        The HCAIF Framework: Five Dimensions
      </Text>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            1. Human Capacity
          </Text>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
            Does your team have the skills to use AI effectively?
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>• Executive AI literacy (can leadership articulate value beyond hype?)</li>
            <li>• Technical capability (in-house expertise vs. vendor dependency)</li>
            <li>• Change leadership capacity (who owns adoption internally?)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            2. Cultural Readiness
          </Text>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
            Will your organization actually adopt what you deploy?
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>• Trust in automation (do staff believe AI recommendations?)</li>
            <li>• Risk tolerance (permission to experiment and fail?)</li>
            <li>• Psychological safety (can staff report AI errors without blame?)</li>
            <li>• Decision-making culture (data-driven vs. intuition-based?)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            3. Adoption Infrastructure
          </Text>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
            Do you have the systems to support AI tools?
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>• Change management capability (structured rollout process?)</li>
            <li>• Training infrastructure (onboarding, ongoing support?)</li>
            <li>• Feedback loops (user input shapes iteration?)</li>
            <li>• Success measurement (how you'll know it's working?)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            4. Integration Feasibility
          </Text>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
            Can AI actually connect to your existing tech stack?
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>• Legacy system compatibility (can it integrate or does it require workarounds?)</li>
            <li>• Data infrastructure (quality, accessibility, governance)</li>
            <li>• API architecture (integration complexity, vendor lock-in risk)</li>
            <li>• Technical debt (migration required before AI works?)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            5. Financial Sustainability
          </Text>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
            Can you afford not just deployment but ongoing optimization?
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>• TCO understanding (beyond license costs: training, integration, support, iteration)</li>
            <li>• Adoption risk in projections (standard ROI vs. reality-adjusted ROI)</li>
            <li>• Continuous improvement budget (AI requires ongoing refinement, not one-time deployment)</li>
            <li>• Success measurement capability (can you actually track ROI post-launch?)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>

  <!-- METHODOLOGY -->
  <section class="border-t border-base-200">
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-16">
      <Text
        tag="h2"
        variant="displayMD"
        class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight font-display"
      >
        Methodology: How the Diagnostic Works
      </Text>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
        <div>
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            Week 1: Discovery & Analysis
          </Text>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-900 font-medium">
                Day 1–3: Structured Interviews (90 minutes each)
              </Text>
              <Text tag="p" variant="textXS" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
                We interview 2–3 stakeholders: Executive sponsor, operational lead, and front-line representative. Using driver tree construction and HCAIF dimension probing.
              </Text>
            </div>

            <div>
              <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-900 font-medium">
                Day 4–5: Analysis
              </Text>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-xs text-base-600">
                <li>• Score each HCAIF dimension (1–10 scale)</li>
                <li>• Build driver trees showing causal relationships</li>
                <li>• Calculate adoption-adjusted ROI</li>
                <li>• Map readiness gaps to business impact</li>
                <li>• Prioritize interventions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            Week 2: Report Development & Delivery
          </Text>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-900 font-medium">
                Day 6–9: Report Writing (9 Pages)
              </Text>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-xs text-base-600">
                <li>• Page 1: Executive summary</li>
                <li>• Page 2: Driver tree visualization</li>
                <li>• Pages 3–7: HCAIF dimension analysis</li>
                <li>• Page 8: Financial impact model</li>
                <li>• Page 9: Implementation roadmap</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-900 font-medium">
                Day 10: Delivery & Debrief (60-minute session)
              </Text>
              <Text tag="p" variant="textXS" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
                Walk through findings, discuss red/yellow/green scores, clarify recommendations, explore next steps.
              </Text>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>

  <!-- DELIVERABLES -->
  <section class="border-t border-base-200 bg-base-50">
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-16">
      <Text
        tag="h2"
        variant="displayMD"
        class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight font-display"
      >
        What You Get: Deliverables
      </Text>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            Primary Deliverable: 9-Page Report
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>✓ Executive summary with primary recommendation</li>
            <li>✓ Driver tree visualization with color-coded readiness assessment</li>
            <li>✓ HCAIF five-dimension assessment (1 page per dimension)</li>
            <li>✓ Financial impact model (standard vs. adoption-adjusted ROI)</li>
            <li>✓ 90-day implementation roadmap</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="text-base-900 font-display">
            Secondary Deliverable
          </Text>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mt-4">
            60-minute debrief session with presentation of findings, Q&A, and discussion of next steps.
          </Text>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="border-t border-base-200">
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <Text
          tag="h2"
          variant="displayMD"
          class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight font-display"
        >
          Investment: $2,500–$4,000
        </Text>

        <div class="mt-8 p-8 bg-base-50 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-900 font-medium">
            What's Included:
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>• 2-week fixed scope (no hourly billing)</li>
            <li>• 2–3 stakeholder interviews (90 minutes each)</li>
            <li>• Driver tree analysis</li>
            <li>• HCAIF five-dimension assessment</li>
            <li>• 9-page diagnostic report</li>
            <li>• 60-minute debrief session</li>
            <li>• Email support during analysis period</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 p-8 bg-base-50 rounded-lg">
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-900 font-medium">
            What's Not Included:
          </Text>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-base-600">
            <li>• Implementation (we assess readiness, we don't build AI systems)</li>
            <li>• Ongoing advisory (that's the Retainer service)</li>
            <li>• Training delivery (that's the Cohort service)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-900 font-medium">
            Payment Terms:
          </Text>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textXS" class="text-base-600 mt-2">
            100% upfront (protects cash flow, signals commitment). Invoice issued upon engagement confirmation. Report delivered within 14 calendar days of kickoff.
          </Text>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-base-200 bg-base-50">
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <Text
          tag="h2"
          variant="displayMD"
          class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight font-display"
        >
          Ready for a readiness assessment?
        </Text>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-8 justify-center">
          <Button
            variant="default"
            size="base"
            isLink={true}
            href="/contact"
          >
            Request Diagnostic Proposal
          </Button>
          <Button
            variant="muted"
            size="base"
            isLink={true}
            href="/contact"
          >
            Schedule Strategic Session
          </Button>
        </div>

        <Button
          variant="muted"
          size="xs"
          isLink={true}
          href="/capabilities"
          class="mt-8"
        >
          ← Back to Services
        </Button>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
